A starter script to get a basic web server up and running on a clean install of Ubuntu.

ROADMAP (in no particular order)
* RVM
* Firewall
* Lock down SSH options
* FTP access
* Mail servers
* Rails
* GIT
* Common host hacks (media temple)
* SVN

Build out different config options for:
* Full stack LAMP server
* MySQL Cluster management server
* MySQL Cluster node
* Apache Load Balancer
* Apache node
* Static file server
* Mail server
* That one server we always meant to build that would monitor all the rest of the servers....
* A server dedicated to handling backups